quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  7,184,"Ṣé wọn kò ronú jinlẹ̀ ni? Kò sí wèrè kan kan lára ẹni wọn (Ànábì Muhammad - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà máa bá a -. Ta sì ni bí kò ṣe olùkìlọ̀ pọ́nńbélé."
  7,185,"Ṣé wọn kò wo ìjọba àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ pẹ̀lú gbogbo n̄ǹkan tí Allāhu dá? Àmọ́ sá ó lè jẹ́ pé Àkókò ikú wọn ti súnmọ́. Nígbà náà, ọ̀rọ̀ wo ni wọn yóò gbàgbọ́ lẹ́yìn rẹ̀?1 {1}",footnotes:1:Gbólóhùn yìí "Nígbà náà, “hadīth wo” ọ̀rọ̀ wo ni wọn yóò gbàgbọ́ lẹ́yìn rẹ̀?" àti irú rẹ̀ tó wà nínú sūrah al-Mursalāt; 77:50 àti sūrah al-Jāthiyah; 45:6, àwọn kan lérò pé ó ń túmọ̀ sí pé, a ò gbọ́dọ̀ gbàgbọ́ nínú hadīth Ànábì kan kan, áḿbọ̀sìbọ́sí pé a óò máa fi ṣe ẹ̀rí ọ̀rọ̀ ẹ̀sìn.
  7,186,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí Allāhu bá ṣì lọ́nà kò lè sí afinimọ̀nà kan fún un. (Allāhu) yó sì fi wọ́n sílẹ̀ sínú àgbéré wọn, tí wọn yóò máa pa rìdàrìdà."
  9,88,"Ṣùgbọ́n Òjíṣẹ́ àti àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo pẹ̀lú rẹ̀, wọ́n fi dúkìá wọn àti ẹ̀mí wọn jagun ẹ̀sìn. Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn, àwọn oore ń bẹ fún wọn. Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn, àwọn sì ni olùjèrè."
  9,89,"Allāhu ti pèsè sílẹ̀ dè wọ́n àwọn Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra kan tí odò ń ṣàn ní ìsàlẹ̀ rẹ̀. Olùṣegbére ni wọ́n nínú rẹ̀. Ìyẹn ni èrèǹjẹ ńlá."
  9,90,"Àwọn aláwàáwí nínú àwọn Lárúbáwá oko wá (bá ọ) nítorí kí wọ́n lè yọ̀ǹda (ìjókòó sílé) fún wọn. Àwọn tó sì pe ọ̀rọ̀ Allāhu àti ọ̀rọ̀ Òjíṣẹ́ nírọ́ náà jókòó sílé. Ọwọ́ ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro máa ba àwọn aláìgbàgbọ́ nínú wọn."
  10,46,"Ó ṣeé ṣe kí A fi apá kan èyí tí A ṣe ní ìlérí fún wọn hàn ọ́ tàbí kí A ti gba ẹ̀mí rẹ (ṣíwájú àsìkò náà), ọ̀dọ̀ Wa kúkú ni ibùpadàsí wọn. Lẹ́yìn náà, Allāhu ni Arínú-róde ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣe níṣẹ́."
  10,47,"Òjíṣẹ́ ti wà fún ìjọ kọ̀ọ̀kan.Nítorí náà, nígbà tí Òjíṣẹ́ wọn bá dé, A óò ṣèdájọ́ láààrin wọn pẹ̀lú déédé; A ò sì níí ṣàbòsí sí wọn. {1}",footnotes:1:Āyah yìí àti tinú sūrah Fātir; 35:24 jẹ́ ọ̀kan nínú ọ̀nà tí ìjọ Ahmadiyyah gbà di kèfèrí. Ìdí ni pé, nítorí àwọn āyah wọ̀nyẹn ni ìjọ náà fi pe gbogbo òrìṣà ní ànábì Ọlọ́hun, àti pé wọ́n gbàgbọ́ pé kò sí ìlú tí Allāhu kò ti gbé òjíṣẹ́ kọ̀ọ̀kan dìde, títí dé ilẹ̀ Yorùbá, ilẹ̀ Haúsá, ilẹ̀ Yíbò àti bẹ́ẹ̀ bẹ́ẹ̀ lọ. Ìtọ́kasí wọn nìyí: “In pursuance of this doctrine, he (mirza Ghulam Ahmad al-Ƙadiyyaaniy) testified to the truth of Krishna, Ram Chandra and Buddha, the prophets of India, and Zoroaster, the prophet of Persia, and described the rejection of their claims as, in a sense, amounting to a denial of the universal Providence of God.” Ìtúmọ̀ “Láti lè tẹ̀lé ìgbàgbọ́ yìí ló mú kí mirza Ghulam Ahmad jẹ́rìí pé òdodo ni òrìṣà Krishna, òrìṣà Ram Chandra àti òrìṣà Buda, tí wọ́n jẹ́ àwọn ànábì ilẹ̀ India. Àti òrìṣà Zoroaster, tí ó jẹ́ ànábì ilẹ̀ Persia. Mirza Ghulam Ahmad sì gbà pé ẹni tí ó bá tako àwọn òrìṣà náà, ó ti tako oore tí Allāhu ṣe fún àgbáyé.” Ahmadiyyah Movement, láti ọwọ́ Bashirud-din Mahmud Ahmad, ojú ewé: 69.
  10,48,"Wọ́n ń wí pé: “Ìgbà wo ni àdéhùn yìí yóò ṣẹ tí ẹ bá jẹ́ olódodo?”"
  11,13,"Tàbí wọ́n ń wí pé: “Ó hun ún ni.” Sọ pé: “Ẹ mú sūrah mẹ́wàá àdáhun bí irú rẹ̀ wá, kí ẹ sì ké sí ẹni tí ẹ bá lè ké sí lẹ́yìn Allāhu tí ẹ bá jẹ́ olódodo.”"
  11,14,"Nígbà náà tí wọn kò bá da yín lóhùn, kí ẹ mọ̀ pé dájúdájú wọ́n sọ (al-Ƙur’ān) kalẹ̀ pẹ̀lú ìmọ̀ Allāhu. Àti pé kò sí ọlọ́hun kan tí a gbọ́dọ̀ jọ́sìn fún ní ọ̀nà òdodo àyàfi Òun. Nítorí náà, ṣé ẹ̀yin yóò di mùsùlùmí?"
  11,15,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá ń fẹ́ ìṣẹ̀mí ayé àti ọ̀ṣọ́ rẹ̀, A óò san wọ́n ní ẹ̀san iṣẹ́ wọn nílé ayé. A ò sì níí dín kiní kan kù fún wọn nílé ayé."